OL,3,CStriking council staff to stage pay
OL,4,Cprotest outside Swinney's office
OL,6,FTrade union members protesting over
OL,7,Fcouncil workers' pay are to take their
OL,8,Ffight to John Swinney's office in a
OL,9,Fbid to encourage the First Minister to
OL,10,Fstep in and end the dispute.
OL,12,FMembers of the Unison union are to
OL,13,Fstage a protest outside Mr Swinney's
OL,14,Fconstituency office in Blairgowrie,
OL,15,FPerthshire, on Thursday.
OL,17,FIt comes as Unison members in the
OL,18,FPerth and Kinross area are taking part
OL,19,Fin a two-week strike which has closed
OL,20,Fa number of schools, with others
OL,21,Fpartially open.
