OL,3,CStriking council staff to stage pay
OL,4,Cprotest outside Swinney's office
OL,6,FThe protest comes despite two other
OL,7,Funions representing council staff,
OL,8,FUnite and GMB Scotland, accepting the
OL,9,Fpay deal offered by local government
OL,10,Fleaders at Cosla.
OL,12,FThat gives workers either a 3.6%
OL,13,Fincrease or a 67p per hour rise,
OL,14,Fwhichever is higher, with the pay deal
OL,15,Fnow imposed on workers.
OL,17,FMr Swinney meanwhile has already
OL,18,Fcondemned the "utterly unacceptable"
OL,19,Ftargeting of his constituency.
