OL,3,CStriking council staff to stage pay
OL,4,Cprotest outside Swinney's office
OL,6,FWith non-teaching school staff taking
OL,7,Fpart in the protest, Mr Swinney said
OL,8,Feducation in his constituency "has
OL,9,Fbeen disrupted".
OL,11,FHe said: "My constituents have been
OL,12,Fsingled out for treatment just because
OL,13,Ftheir MSP is First Minister, and I
OL,14,Ffind that completely unacceptable."
