OL,3,CStriking council staff to stage pay
OL,4,Cprotest outside Swinney's office
OL,6,FBut Unison Perth and Kinross branch
OL,7,Fsecretary Stuart Hope insisted the
OL,8,FFirst Minister could end the dispute
OL,9,Fby providing further cash for councils
OL,10,Fto fund workers' pay ` despite Mr
OL,11,FSwinney having already declared there
OL,12,Fis no more money available.
OL,14,FMr Hope said: "John Swinney is the one
OL,15,Fwho can end this dispute as most
OL,16,Fcouncil funding comes from the
OL,17,FScottish Government.
OL,19,F"Education staff do not want to close
OL,20,Fschools. They all love their jobs and
OL,21,Fwould prefer to be supporting children.
