OL,6,F"The way to solve this is for Cosla,
OL,7,Fthe Scottish Government and the union
OL,8,Fto sit down in the same room and talk.
OL,10,F"Staff need to be valued and treated
OL,11,Fequally to other public sector workers
OL,12,Fwith the same level of investment."
OL,14,FFinance and Local Government Secretary
OL,15,FShona Robison said: "While this
OL,16,FGovernment respects workers' rights,
OL,17,Fno one's interests are served by
OL,18,Findustrial action which disrupts
OL,19,Fchildren and young people attending
OL,20,Fschools and nurseries in Perth and
OL,21,FKinross.
