OL,6,F"I very much appreciate and understand
OL,7,Fparents' concerns. I want to assure
OL,8,Fthem that we worked hard over the
OL,9,Fsummer with Cosla and the unions to
OL,10,Fagree a pay deal. The deal means that
OL,11,Fthe lowest paid council workers,
OL,12,Fincluding Unison members, receive a
OL,13,F5.63% pay increase.
