OL,6,F"It is a fair pay deal, and I hope
OL,7,Fthat Unison members will now join
OL,8,Ftheir GMB and Unite colleagues and
OL,9,Faccept it and end these unnecessary
OL,10,Fstrikes. Now that local government
OL,11,Fworkers in England have agreed a lower
OL,12,Fpay deal, it's difficult to understand
OL,13,Fwhy this action is continuing."
OL,15,FCosla has been contacted for comment.
